{"id":53,"parent_id":30,"book_id":95,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":53,"title":"2 Nephi 23","subtitle":"","short_title":"2 Ne.","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/23","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 23"],[".studySummary",["i","The destruction of Babylon is a type of the destruction at the Second Coming—It will be a day of wrath and vengeance—Babylon (the world) will fall forever—Compare",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/13"},"Isaiah 13"],". About 559–545",["span.small","B.C."]]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/23.1","order":"05.13.023.5559"},["b","1"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"The burden"],"of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"Babylon"],", which Isaiah the son of Amoz did see."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/23.2","order":"05.13.023.5560"},["b","2"],"Lift ye up a banner upon the high mountain, exalt the voice unto them,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"shake the hand"],", that they may go into the gates of the nobles."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/23.3","order":"05.13.023.5561"},["b","3"],"I have commanded my sanctified ones, I have also called my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"mighty"],"ones, for mine anger is not upon them that rejoice in my highness."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/23.4","order":"05.13.023.5562"},["b","4"],"The noise of the multitude in the mountains like as of a great people, a tumultuous noise of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"kingdoms"],"of nations",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"gathered"],"together, the Lord of Hosts mustereth the hosts of the battle."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/23.5","order":"05.13.023.5563"},["b","5"],"They come from a far country, from the end of heaven, yea, the Lord, and the weapons of his indignation, to destroy the whole land."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/23.6","order":"05.13.023.5564"},["b","6"],"Howl ye, for the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"day"],"of the Lord is at hand; it shall come as a destruction from the Almighty."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/23.7","order":"05.13.023.5565"},["b","7"],"Therefore shall all hands be faint, every man’s heart shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"melt"],";"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/23.8","order":"05.13.023.5566"},["b","8"],"And they shall be afraid; pangs and sorrows shall take hold of them; they shall be amazed one at another; their faces shall be as flames."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/23.9","order":"05.13.023.5567"},["b","9"],"Behold, the day of the Lord cometh, cruel both with wrath and fierce anger, to lay the land desolate; and he shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"destroy"],"the sinners thereof out of it."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/23.10","order":"05.13.023.5568"},["b","10"],"For the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"stars"],"of heaven and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"constellations"],"thereof shall not give their",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"light"],"; the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_10d"},"sun"],"shall be darkened in his going forth, and the moon shall not cause her light to shine."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/23.11","order":"05.13.023.5569"},["b","11"],"And I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"punish"],"the world for evil, and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"wicked"],"for their iniquity; I will cause the arrogancy of the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"proud"],"to cease, and will lay down the haughtiness of the terrible."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/23.12","order":"05.13.023.5570"},["b","12"],"I will make a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"man"],"more precious than fine gold; even a man than the golden wedge of Ophir."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/23.13","order":"05.13.023.5571"},["b","13"],"Therefore, I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"shake"],"the heavens, and the earth shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"remove"],"out of her place, in the wrath of the Lord of Hosts, and in the day of his fierce anger."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/23.14","order":"05.13.023.5572"},["b","14"],"And it shall be as the chased roe, and as a sheep that no man taketh up; and they shall every man turn to his own people, and flee every one into his own",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"land"],"."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/23.15","order":"05.13.023.5573"},["b","15"],"Every one that is proud shall be thrust through; yea, and every one that is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"joined"],"to the wicked shall fall by the sword."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/23.16","order":"05.13.023.5574"},["b","16"],"Their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"children"],"also shall be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"dashed"],"to pieces before their eyes; their houses shall be spoiled and their wives ravished."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/23.17","order":"05.13.023.5575"},["b","17"],"Behold, I will stir up the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"Medes"],"against them, which shall not regard silver and gold, nor shall they delight in it."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/23.18","order":"05.13.023.5576"},["b","18"],"Their bows shall also dash the young men to pieces; and they shall have no",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"pity"],"on the fruit of the womb; their eyes shall not spare children."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/23.19","order":"05.13.023.5577"},["b","19"],"And",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"Babylon"],", the glory of kingdoms, the beauty of the Chaldees’ excellency, shall be as when God overthrew",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"Sodom"],"and Gomorrah."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/23.20","order":"05.13.023.5578"},["b","20"],"It shall never be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"inhabited"],", neither shall it be dwelt in from generation to generation: neither shall the Arabian pitch tent there; neither shall the shepherds make their fold there."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/23.21","order":"05.13.023.5579"},["b","21"],"But",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"wild"],"beasts of the desert shall lie there; and their houses shall be full of doleful creatures; and owls shall dwell there, and satyrs shall dance there."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/23.22","order":"05.13.023.5580"},["b","22"],"And the wild beasts of the islands shall cry in their desolate houses, and dragons in their pleasant palaces; and her time is near to come, and her day shall not be prolonged. For I will destroy her speedily; yea, for I will be merciful unto my people, but the wicked shall perish."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/23.1a","order":"05.13.023.5581"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/13.1.1-22"},"Isa. 13:1 (1–22)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/23.1b","order":"05.13.023.5583"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/babylon"},"TG Babylon"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/23.2a","order":"05.13.023.5585"},["b","2a"],["span.small","IE"],"wave the hand, give a signal."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/23.3a","order":"05.13.023.5587"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.11"},"Joel 3:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/23.4a","order":"05.13.023.5589"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.14.11,14"},"Joel 3:14 (11, 14)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.8"},"Zeph. 3:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zech/14.2.2-3"},"Zech. 14:2 (2–3)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/23.4b","order":"05.13.023.5591"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zech/12.3.2-9"},"Zech. 12:3 (2–9)"],"."],[